asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Riot Grrrl
description:
Lead singer for all female punk rock band 'Thumper', best known for their hit track 'Buck Shot', Riot Grrrl is the face of the modern Doe Movement that is escaping the burrows and challenging the 70 percent.
When she is not recording and performing with Thumper, she is steadily making a name for herself in the underground electronic music scene.  Performing powerful House  Techno beats under her DJ name 'Doeminatrix', club hit 'Lucky Foot' can be heard reverberating from every Nimbus in the Metaverse.  Her thumping beats are building a captivated following amongst the Mycelium crew, and she can be found playing the hottest VIP parties in the psychedelic burrows of The Underground.
Although music is her 'carrot on a stick', Riot Grrrl is also chasing her dreams of breaking into the film industry, hopping on any opportunity to get her foot in the door and kick some buck ****.
She is said to be a devotee to the mysterious Cult of Flufthulu but refuses to comment publicly on the matter.
Riot Grrrl is a doe on a mission and one to watch!
